text: Alive As Fuck was released in 2009. It is the first live album by the Nashville, TN rock band, Black Diamond Heavies. This album was recorded during their show at the Masonic Lodge, in Covington, KY and was released under the Alive Records label.All Music Black Diamond Heavies Alive as Fuck: Masonic Lodge, Covington, KYPlug In Music Black Diamond Heavies Alive as Fuck ==Track listing== ==References== ==External links== Category:2009 albums Category:Black Diamond Heavies albums Category:Alive Naturalsound Records albums
